description:
(2017)

This is a short film about spiritual perception. You can define it as a mental illness, or it is a poem:

I am my own existence, my will is the hand that drags the horse of substance;

I choose to live 9 inches of life instead of 2, and my sense of feeling grow 7 inches more too;

My will is a running fugitive for time and space, regardless of that chain on my chin.



